31 15.3408L9.2168 15.2305C9.36965 15.1046 9.55583 14.9207 9.90527 14.5713L14.8926 9.58301L11.666 6.35742L6.67871 11.3447ZM16.1963 5.05371C15.3054 4.16304 13.8616 4.16305 12.9707 5.05371L12.6074 5.41602L15.833 8.64258L16.1963 8.2793C17.0869 7.38845 17.0869 5.94456 16.1963 5.05371Z"></path><path d="M4.58301 1.7832C4.72589 1.7832 4.84877 1.88437 4.87695 2.02441C4.99384 2.60873 5.22432 3.11642 5.58398 3.50391C5.94115 3.88854 6.44253 4.172 7.13281 4.28711C7.27713 4.3114 7.38267 4.43665 7.38281 4.58301C7.38281 4.7295 7.27723 4.8546 7.13281 4.87891C6.44249 4.99401 5.94116 5.27746 5.58398 5.66211C5.26908 6.00126 5.05404 6.43267 4.92676 6.92676L4.87695 7.1416C4.84891 7.28183 4.72601 7.38281 4.58301 7.38281C4.44013 7.38267 4.31709 7.28173 4.28906 7.1416C4.17212 6.55728 3.94179 6.04956 3.58203 5.66211C3.22483 5.27757 2.72347 4.99395 2.0332 4.87891C1.88897 4.85446 1.7832 4.72938 1.7832 4.58301C1.78335 4.43673 1.88902 4.3115 2.0332 4.28711C2.72366 4.17203 3.22481 3.88861 3.58203 3.50391C3.94186 3.11638 4.17214 2.60888 4.28906 2.02441L4.30371 1.97363C4.34801 1.86052 4.45804 1.78333 4.58301 1.7832Z"></path></svg>Edit</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-powershell"><span>wsl --install
</span></code></div></div></pre>
<ol start="2" data-start="975" data-end="1069">
<li data-start="975" data-end="1018">
<p data-start="978" data-end="1018"><strong data-start="978" data-end="1018">Install Ubuntu from Microsoft Store.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1019" data-end="1069">
<p data-start="1022" data-end="1069"><strong data-start="1022" data-end="1069">Set the default terminal in VS Code to WSL:</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="1070" data-end="1194">
<li data-start="1070" data-end="1111">
<p data-start="1072" data-end="1111">Go to <strong data-start="1078" data-end="1111">File &gt; Preferences &gt; Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1112" data-end="1173">
<p data-start="1114" data-end="1173">Search for <strong data-start="1125" data-end="1173">"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows"</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1174" data-end="1194">
<p data-start="1176" data-end="1194">Set it to <strong data-start="1186" data-end="1193">WSL</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1196" data-end="1238">Now, your VS Code terminal will look like:</p>
