<h2 data-start="1279" data-end="1319">✅ <strong data-start="1284" data-end="1319">3. Configure Git Name and Email</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1320" data-end="1395">Run these commands in your terminal (PowerShell or Ubuntu/WSL — both work):</p>
