<hr data-start="1802" data-end="1805">
<h2 data-start="1807" data-end="1859">✅ <strong data-start="1812" data-end="1859">4. Step-by-Step to Push a Project to GitHub</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1860" data-end="1915">Here’s a <strong data-start="1869" data-end="1893">clear complete guide</strong> to push your project:</p>
<h3 data-start="1917" data-end="1989">📌 <strong data-start="1924" data-end="1935">Step 1:</strong> Create a new repo on GitHub (no README or .gitignore)</h3>
<ul data-start="1990" data-end="2033">
<li data-start="1990" data-end="2033">
<p data-start="1992" data-end="2033">Example repo name: <strong data-start="2011" data-end="2033">My_First_Portfolio</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2035" data-end="2038">
