git push -u origin main
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2737" data-end="2797">✅ <strong data-start="2739" data-end="2797">Check your GitHub — your project should now be online!</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2799" data-end="2802">
<h2 data-start="2804" data-end="2848">✅ <strong data-start="2809" data-end="2848">5. Configure VS Code Git (Optional)</strong></h2>
<p data-start="2849" data-end="2907">If VS Code asks for authentication when pushing to GitHub:</p>
<ul data-start="2908" data-end="3041">
<li data-start="2908" data-end="3041">
<p data-start="2910" data-end="3041"><strong data-start="2910" data-end="2926">Best method:</strong> Use <strong data-start="2931" data-end="2938">SSH</strong> or <strong data-start="2942" data-end="2980">GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT)</strong> for authentication.<br>
If you want, I’ll guide you on that too.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3043" data-end="3046">
<h2 data-start="3048" data-end="3087">✅ <strong data-start="3053" data-end="3087">Summary of What You Need to Do</strong></h2>
<div class="_tableContainer_16hzy_1"><div tabindex="-1" class="_tableWrapper_16hzy_14 group flex w-fit flex-col-reverse"><table data-start="3088" data-end="4095" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="3088" data-end="3200"><tr data-start="3088" data-end="3200"><th data-start="3088" data-end="3120" data-col-size="sm">Task</th><th data-start="3120" data-end="3200" data-col-size="md">Command/Step</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="3312" data-end="4095"><tr data-start="3312" data-end="3422"><td data-start="3312" data-end="3344" data-col-size="sm">Install WSL (Ubuntu Terminal)</td><td data-start="3344" data-end="3422" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3346" data-end="3361">wsl --install</code> (in PowerShell)</td></tr><tr data-start="3423" data-end="3545"><td data-start="3423" data-end="3455" data-col-size="sm">Configure Git name/email</td><td data-start="3455" data-end="3545" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3457" data-end="3500">git config --global user.name "Your Name"</code> + <code data-start="3503" data-end="3543">git config --global user.email "email"</code></td></tr><tr data-start="3546" data-end="3655"><td data-start="3546" data-end="3578" data-col-size="sm">Initialize Git in project</td><td data-start="3578" data-end="3655" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3580" data-end="3590">git init</code></td></tr><tr data-start="3656" data-end="3765"><td data-start="3656" data-end="3688" data-col-size="sm">Add files</td><td data-start="3688" data-end="3765" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3690" data-end="3701">git add .</code></td></tr><tr data-start="3766" data-end="3875"><td data-start="3766" data-end="3798" data-col-size="sm">Commit</td><td data-start="3798" data-end="3875" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3800" data-end="3832">git commit -m "Initial commit"</code></td></tr><tr data-start="3876" data-end="3985"><td data-start="3876" data-end="3908" data-col-size="sm">Link GitHub repo</td><td data-start="3908" data-end="3985" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="3910" data-end="3975">git remote add origin https://github.com/username/repo-name.git</code></td></tr><tr data-start="3986" data-end="4095"><td data-start="3986" data-end="4018" data-col-size="sm">Push to GitHub</td><td data-start="4018" data-end="4095" data-col-size="md"><code data-start="4020" data-end="4045">git push -u origin main</code></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky end-(--thread-content-margin) h-0 self-end select-none"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="bg-token-bg-primary hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 9.95614 12.668 9.46258 12.6367 9.0791C12.6137 8.79732 12.5758 8.60761 12.5244 8.46387L12.4688 8.33399C12.3148 8.03193 12.0803 7.77885 11.793 7.60254L11.666 7.53125C11.508 7.45087 11.2963 7.39395 10.9209 7.36328C10.5374 7.33197 10.0439 7.33203 9.33301 7.33203H6.5C5.78896 7.33203 5.29563 7.33195 4.91211 7.36328C4.63016 7.38632 4.44065 7.42413 4.29688 7.47559L4.16699 7.53125C3.86488 7.68518 3.61186 7.9196 3.43555 8.20703L3.36524 8.33399C3.28478 8.49198 3.22795 8.70352 3.19727 9.0791C3.16595 9.46259 3.16504 9.95611 3.16504 10.667V13.5C3.16504 14.211 3.16593 14.7044 3.19727 15.0879C3.22797 15.4636 3.28473 15.675 3.36524 15.833L3.43555 15.959C3.61186 16.2466 3.86474 16.4807 4.16699 16.6348L4.29688 16.6914C4.44063 16.7428 4.63025 16.7797 4.91211 16.8027C5.29563 16.8341 5.78896 16.835 6.5 16.835H9.33301C10.0439 16.835 10.5374 16.8341 10.9209 16.8027C11.2965 16.772 11.508 16.7152 11.666 16.6348L11.793 16.5645C12.0804 16.3881 12.3148 16.1351 12.4688 15.833L12.5244 15.7031C12.5759 15.5594 12.6137 15.3698 12.6367 15.0879C12