9.42091 1.87109 8.9707C1.90851 8.5127 1.98772 8.10625 2.17969 7.72949L2.30176 7.51172C2.60586 7.0159 3.04236 6.6122 3.56348 6.34668L3.70606 6.28027C4.04237 6.136 4.40303 6.07083 4.80371 6.03809C5.14051 6.01057 5.53708 6.00551 6.00391 6.00391C6.00551 5.53708 6.01057 5.14051 6.03809 4.80371C6.0755 4.34588 6.15483 3.94012 6.34668 3.56348L6.46875 3.34473C6.77282 2.84912 7.20856 2.44514 7.72949 2.17969L7.87207 2.11328C8.20855 1.96886 8.56979 1.90385 8.9707 1.87109C9.42091 1.83432 9.978 1.83496 10.667 1.83496H13.5C14.1891 1.83496 14.746 1.83431 15.1963 1.87109C15.6541 1.90851 16.0599 1.98788 16.4365 2.17969L16.6553 2.30176C17.151 2.60585 17.5548 3.04244 17.8203 3.56348L17.8867 3.70606C18.031 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="4097" data-end="4100">
<p data-start="4102" data-end="4239">✅ <strong data-start="4104" data-end="4196">Do you want help installing WSL or setting up SSH keys or PAT for GitHub authentication?</strong><br data-start="4196" data-end="4199">
Just tell me — I’ll walk you through it.</p>
<p data-start="4241" data-end="4330" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Let me know if you want me to prepare the <strong data-start="4283" data-end="4329">exact commands customized for your project</strong>.</p></div></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="87e3b702-880a-4049-bbd8-4ce7165f331e" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="54">Thank you for explaining clearly. That specific error:</p>
<blockquote data-start="56" data-end="160">
<p data-start="58" data-end="160"><strong data-start="58" data-end="160">“The terminal process ‘C:\Windows\System32\bash.exe' -d ubuntu-22.0' terminated with exit code: 2”</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="162" data-end="282">— usually happens when <strong data-start="185" data-end="201">Ubuntu (WSL)</strong> is <strong data-start="205" data-end="238">either not installed properly</strong> or <strong data-start="242" data-end="281">the name of the distro is incorrect</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="284" data-end="318">Let’s solve it <strong data-start="299" data-end="315">step-by-step</strong> 👇</p>
<hr data-start="320" data-end="323">
<h2 data-start="325" data-end="372">✅ STEP 1: Check if WSL is Installed Properly</h2>
<h3 data-start="374" data-end="430">1️⃣ Open <strong data-start="387" data-end="405">Command Prompt</strong> (CMD), <em data-start="413" data-end="418">not</em> PowerShell.</h3>
<p data-start="431" data-end="484">Press <code data-start="437" data-end="450">Windows + R</code>, type <code data-start="457" data-end="462">cmd</code>, and press <strong data-start="474" data-end="483">Enter</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="486" data-end="496">Now, type:</p>
