* Ubuntu</span><span><span class="hljs-number">-22.04</span></span><span>    Running         </span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="678" data-end="759">OR you may see <strong data-start="693" data-end="704">nothing</strong>, or an error → meaning <strong data-start="728" data-end="758">Ubuntu isn’t installed yet</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="761" data-end="764">
<h2 data-start="766" data-end="814">✅ STEP 2: Install Ubuntu Properly (If Needed)</h2>
<p data-start="816" data-end="873">If <strong data-start="819" data-end="835">Ubuntu-22.04</strong> or any version doesn’t show, do this:</p>
