</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="902" data-end="923">Or manually download:</p>
<ol data-start="925" data-end="1116">
<li data-start="925" data-end="964">
<p data-start="928" data-end="964">Open <strong data-start="933" data-end="952">Microsoft Store</strong> on Windows.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="965" data-end="1017">
<p data-start="968" data-end="1017">Search for <strong data-start="979" data-end="991">“Ubuntu”</strong> (e.g., Ubuntu 22.04 LTS).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1018" data-end="1039">
<p data-start="1021" data-end="1039">Click <strong data-start="1027" data-end="1038">Install</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1040" data-end="1116">
<p data-start="1043" data-end="1116">After installation → <strong data-start="1064" data-end="1074">launch</strong> Ubuntu, <strong data-start="1083" data-end="1115">set your username &amp; password</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1118" data-end="1148">✅ Once installed, check again:</p>
