    </span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-attr">"terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.windows"</span></span><span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Ubuntu"</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1970" data-end="1973">
<h2 data-start="1975" data-end="1992">✅ STEP 5: Test</h2>
<p data-start="1994" data-end="2027">Now click <code data-start="2004" data-end="2007">+</code> for a new terminal.</p>
