</span></span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2119" data-end="2122">
<h2 data-start="2124" data-end="2153">❗ WHY THAT ERROR HAPPENED:</h2>
<ul data-start="2154" data-end="2342">
<li data-start="2154" data-end="2283">
<p data-start="2156" data-end="2283"><strong data-start="2156" data-end="2171">Exit code 2</strong> usually means <strong data-start="2186" data-end="2213">wrong distribution name</strong> (<code data-start="2215" data-end="2228">ubuntu-22.0</code> is invalid; correct one is <code data-start="2256" data-end="2270">Ubuntu-22.04</code> or similar).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2284" data-end="2342">
<p data-start="2286" data-end="2342">It also happens if Ubuntu isn’t <strong data-start="2318" data-end="2341">fully installed yet</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2344" data-end="2347">
<h2 data-start="2349" data-end="2385">⚙️ EXTRA: Confirm Git Setup Again</h2>
