<hr data-start="808" data-end="811">
<h3 data-start="813" data-end="846">✅ <strong data-start="819" data-end="846">Which one should I use?</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="847" data-end="968">
<li data-start="847" data-end="885">
<p data-start="849" data-end="885">👉 <strong data-start="852" data-end="859">CMD</strong> (Command Prompt) = SIMPLE</p>
</li>
<li data-start="886" data-end="931">
<p data-start="888" data-end="931">👉 <strong data-start="891" data-end="905">PowerShell</strong> = ADVANCED (but okay too)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="932" data-end="968">
<p data-start="934" data-end="968">👉 Both work for <strong data-start="951" data-end="958">wsl</strong> commands.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="970" data-end="1048"><strong data-start="970" data-end="998">Use whichever you prefer</strong> — <strong data-start="1001" data-end="1039">I recommend CMD to avoid confusion</strong> for now.</p>
