5.3408L9.2168 15.2305C9.36965 15.1046 9.55583 14.9207 9.90527 14.5713L14.8926 9.58301L11.666 6.35742L6.67871 11.3447ZM16.1963 5.05371C15.3054 4.16304 13.8616 4.16305 12.9707 5.05371L12.6074 5.41602L15.833 8.64258L16.1963 8.2793C17.0869 7.38845 17.0869 5.94456 16.1963 5.05371Z"></path><path d="M4.58301 1.7832C4.72589 1.7832 4.84877 1.88437 4.87695 2.02441C4.99384 2.60873 5.22432 3.11642 5.58398 3.50391C5.94115 3.88854 6.44253 4.172 7.13281 4.28711C7.27713 4.3114 7.38267 4.43665 7.38281 4.58301C7.38281 4.7295 7.27723 4.8546 7.13281 4.87891C6.44249 4.99401 5.94116 5.27746 5.58398 5.66211C5.26908 6.00126 5.05404 6.43267 4.92676 6.92676L4.87695 7.1416C4.84891 7.28183 4.72601 7.38281 4.58301 7.38281C4.44013 7.38267 4.31709 7.28173 4.28906 7.1416C4.17212 6.55728 3.94179 6.04956 3.58203 5.66211C3.22483 5.27757 2.72347 4.99395 2.0332 4.87891C1.88897 4.85446 1.7832 4.72938 1.7832 4.58301C1.78335 4.43673 1.88902 4.3115 2.0332 4.28711C2.72366 4.17203 3.22481 3.88861 3.58203 3.50391C3.94186 3.11638 4.17214 2.60888 4.28906 2.02441L4.30371 1.97363C4.34801 1.86052 4.45804 1.78333 4.58301 1.7832Z"></path></svg>Edit</button></span></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-bash"><span><span>wsl --install
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1909" data-end="1915"><strong data-start="1909" data-end="1915">OR</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1916" data-end="1975">
<li data-start="1916" data-end="1975">
<p data-start="1918" data-end="1975">Go to <strong data-start="1924" data-end="1975">Microsoft Store → Search “Ubuntu” → Install it.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1977" data-end="1980">
<h3 data-start="1982" data-end="1997">Step 2️⃣:</h3>
<p data-start="1998" data-end="2047">After Ubuntu is installed, <strong data-start="2025" data-end="2047">you can use it in:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="2048" data-end="2133">
<li data-start="2048" data-end="2084">
<p data-start="2050" data-end="2084">✅ Windows search (type <strong data-start="2073" data-end="2083">Ubuntu</strong>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2085" data-end="2133">
<p data-start="2087" data-end="2133">✅ VS Code terminal → choose Ubuntu as terminal</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2135" data-end="2138">
<p data-start="2140" data-end="2239">Let’s start from <strong data-start="2157" data-end="2167">Step 1</strong>.<br data-start="2168" data-end="2171">
