her to help you find <strong data-start="79" data-end="100">Terminal settings</strong> in VS Code.</p>
<p data-start="114" data-end="199">I’ll show you <strong data-start="128" data-end="146">two clear ways</strong> to change the terminal to <strong data-start="173" data-end="183">Ubuntu</strong> inside VS Code.</p>
<hr data-start="201" data-end="204">
<h2 data-start="206" data-end="250">✅ <strong data-start="211" data-end="250">Method 1: Using the Command Palette</strong></h2>
