<p data-start="516" data-end="555">It should now open <strong data-start="535" data-end="545">Ubuntu</strong> terminal.</p>
<hr data-start="557" data-end="560">
<h2 data-start="562" data-end="599">✅ <strong data-start="567" data-end="599">Method 2: Using Settings GUI</strong></h2>
