<hr data-start="1586" data-end="1589">
<h2 data-start="1591" data-end="1642">⚠️ Still showing “terminated with exit code: 2”?</h2>
<p data-start="1644" data-end="1694">If <strong data-start="1647" data-end="1679">it’s still showing the error</strong>, follow these:</p>
<p data-start="1696" data-end="1735">1️⃣ Open CMD → <strong data-start="1711" data-end="1734">Run Ubuntu manually</strong>:</p>
