</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1768" data-end="1868">➡️ If that works in CMD but not VS Code → <strong data-start="1810" data-end="1842">it’s a VS Code profile issue</strong> → recheck the JSON above.</p>
<p data-start="1870" data-end="1990">2️⃣ <strong data-start="1874" data-end="1908">If it doesn’t work even in CMD</strong> → Something is wrong with the WSL installation → we may need to <strong data-start="1973" data-end="1989">reset Ubuntu</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1992" data-end="1995">
<h3 data-start="1997" data-end="2047">✅ <strong data-start="2003" data-end="2032">To Reset Ubuntu if broken</strong> (last resort):</h3>
<ol data-start="2049" data-end="2220">
<li data-start="2049" data-end="2162">
<p data-start="2052" data-end="2162"><strong data-start="2052" data-end="2162">Windows key → search → Apps → Installed Apps → Find “Ubuntu 22.04 LTS” → Click → Advanced Options → Reset.</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2164" data-end="2220">
<p data-start="2167" data-end="2220">OR <strong data-start="2170" data-end="2220">Uninstall it → Reinstall from Microsoft Store.</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="2222" data-end="2225">
<h2 data-start="2227" data-end="2244">✅ <strong data-start="2232" data-end="2244">Summary:</strong></h2>
<div class="_tableContainer_16hzy_1"><div tabindex="-1" class="_tableWrapper_16hzy_14 group flex w-fit flex-col-reverse"><table data-start="2245" data-end="2528" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="2245" data-end="2279"><tr data-start="2245" data-end="2279"><th data-start="2245" data-end="2268" data-col-size="sm">Task</th><th data-start="2268" data-end="2279" data-col-size="sm">Status</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="2315" data-end="2528"><tr data-start="2315" data-end="2363"><td data-start="2315" data-end="2338" data-col-size="sm">Confirm distro name</td><td data-start="2338" data-end="2363" data-col-size="sm">✅ Done (Ubuntu-22.04)</td></tr><tr data-start="2364" data-end="2406"><td data-start="2364" data-end="2387" data-col-size="sm">Fix VS Code JSON</td><td data-start="2387" data-end="2406" data-col-size="sm">⚙ Working on it</td></tr><tr data-start="2407" data-end="2469"><td data-start="2407" data-end="2430" data-col-size="sm">Confirm CMD works</td><td data-start="2430" data-end="2469" data-col-size="sm">🔧 Check with <code data-start="2446" data-end="2467">wsl -d Ubuntu-22.04</code></td></tr><tr data-start="2470" data-end="2528"><td data-start="2470" data-end="2493" data-col-size="sm">Reset if necessary</td><td data-start="2493" data-end="2528" data-col-size="sm">❗ Optional only if still broken</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky end-(--thread-content-margin) h-0 self-end select-none"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 32.7969px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button class="bg-token-bg-primary hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 9.95614 12.668 9.46258 12.6367 9.0791C12.6137 8.79732 12.5758