<ul data-start="400" data-end="543">
<li data-start="400" data-end="451">
<p data-start="402" data-end="451">✅ Make it <strong data-start="412" data-end="422">Public</strong> or <strong data-start="426" data-end="437">Private</strong> (your choice)</p>
