</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span></span><span> techcon_website
</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span></span><span> techcon_website
</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">touch</span></span><span> index.html
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="738" data-end="758">Or do it in VS Code:</p>
<ul data-start="759" data-end="862">
<li data-start="759" data-end="777">
<p data-start="761" data-end="777">Open <strong data-start="766" data-end="777">VS Code</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="778" data-end="826">
<p data-start="780" data-end="826">Go to <strong data-start="786" data-end="826">File → Open Folder → techcon_website</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="827" data-end="862">
<p data-start="829" data-end="862">Create a new file: <strong data-start="848" data-end="862">index.html</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="864" data-end="867">
