sage+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="116">Excellent — let’s <strong data-start="18" data-end="48">work together step-by-step</strong> to complete this <strong data-start="66" data-end="93">About Page (about.html)</strong> for <strong data-start="98" data-end="114">TechCon 2024</strong> ✅</p>
<p data-start="118" data-end="231">Here’s a <strong data-start="127" data-end="146">clear breakdown</strong>, including the <strong data-start="162" data-end="175">HTML code</strong> you can use directly, and how to <strong data-start="209" data-end="230">push it to GitHub</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="233" data-end="236">
<h2 data-start="238" data-end="281">✅ <strong data-start="243" data-end="281">STEP 1: Create the about.html File</strong></h2>
<p data-start="282" data-end="320">In your <strong data-start="290" data-end="309">techcon_website</strong> directory:</p>
