        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h1</span></span></span><span>&gt;About TechCon 2024</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h1</span></span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">nav</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">ul</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"index.html"</span></span><span>&gt;Home</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"schedule.html"</span></span><span>&gt;Schedule</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"register.html"</span></span><span>&gt;Register</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">href</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"contact.html"</span></span><span>&gt;Contact</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">a</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">li</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">ul</span></span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">nav</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">header</span></span></span><span>&gt;

    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">main</span></span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- History Section --&gt;</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;Our History</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;Since its inception in 2010, TechCon has grown from a small meetup of tech enthusiasts to a global conference attracting thousands of participants each year.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"images/history.jpg"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Early TechCon Event"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">width</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"500"</span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;

        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- Mission Section --&gt;</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;Our Mission</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;TechCon is dedicated to promoting innovation, connecting tech leaders with emerging talents, and driving technological solutions for global challenges.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"images/mission.jpg"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Team brainstorming session"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">width</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"500"</span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;

        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- Past Speakers Section --&gt;</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;Notable Past Speakers</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h2</span></span></span><span>&gt;

            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">section</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h3</span></span></span><span>&gt;Jane Doe</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h3</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"images/jane_doe.jpg"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Jane Doe speaking at TechCon 2022"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">width</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"200"</span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;Jane is a renowned AI researcher and has been instrumental in shaping ethical AI policies worldwide.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">section</span></span></span><span>&gt;

            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">section</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">h3</span></span></span><span>&gt;John Smith</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">h3</span></span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">img</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">src</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"images/john_smith.jpg"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">alt</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"John Smith keynote speech"</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">width</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"200"</span></span><span>&gt;
                </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;John is a tech entrepreneur known for his contributions to cloud computing and digital transformation strategies.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">section</span></span></span><span>&gt;

        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">article</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">main</span></span></span><span>&gt;

    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">footer</span></span></span><span>&gt;
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-symbol">&amp;copy;</span></span><span> 2024 TechCon. All rights reserved.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">footer</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">body</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">html</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2735" data-end="2817">✅ <strong data-start="2737" data-end="2780">Place your images in an <code data-start="2763" data-end="2771">images</code> folder</strong> inside <code data-start="2788" data-end="2806">techcon_website/</code> directory.</p>
