 data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="97">Perfect — here’s a <strong data-start="19" data-end="33">full guide</strong> and <strong data-start="38" data-end="55">complete code</strong> for your <strong data-start="65" data-end="95">TechCon 2024 schedule.html</strong> ✅</p>
<p data-start="99" data-end="171">We’ll do <strong data-start="108" data-end="119">exactly</strong> what’s required in the <strong data-start="143" data-end="170">assignment instructions</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="173" data-end="176">
<h1 data-start="178" data-end="223">✅ <strong data-start="182" data-end="223">STEP 1: Create the schedule.html File</strong></h1>
<p data-start="225" data-end="253">In your terminal or VS Code:</p>
