<p data-start="3682" data-end="3854" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Let me know when you’re ready for <strong data-start="3716" data-end="3736">3. Register page</strong> or <strong data-start="3740" data-end="3759">4. Contact page</strong>, and I’ll help with those next.<br data-start="3791" data-end="3794">
