        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">tr</span></span></span><span>&gt;
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">scope</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"col"</span></span><span>&gt;Time</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span>&gt;     ✅ REQUIRED
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">scope</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"col"</span></span><span>&gt;Session</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span>&gt;  ✅ REQUIRED
            </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-attr">scope</span></span><span>=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"col"</span></span><span>&gt;Speaker</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">th</span></span></span><span>&gt;  ✅ REQUIRED
        </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">tr</span></span></span><span>&gt;
    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">thead</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1299" data-end="1302">
<h3 data-start="1304" data-end="1341">4️⃣ <strong data-start="1312" data-end="1341">Footer Text Inconsistency</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1342" data-end="1420">
<li data-start="1342" data-end="1420">
<p data-start="1344" data-end="1420">The footer <strong data-start="1355" data-end="1402">must be exactly the same as in <code data-start="1388" data-end="1400">index.html</code></strong> and <code data-start="1407" data-end="1419">about.html</code>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1422" data-end="1430">Example:</p>
