text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="99">Thanks for sharing your code — I just <strong data-start="38" data-end="66">reviewed it line by line</strong>, and here’s the honest analysis:</p>
<hr data-start="101" data-end="104">
<h2 data-start="106" data-end="125">✅ <strong data-start="111" data-end="125">Good News:</strong></h2>
<ul data-start="126" data-end="286">
<li data-start="126" data-end="160">
<p data-start="128" data-end="160"><strong data-start="128" data-end="160">Overall structure is correct</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="161" data-end="216">
<p data-start="163" data-end="216"><code data-start="163" data-end="173">&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code data-start="175" data-end="182">&lt;nav&gt;</code>, <code data-start="184" data-end="192">&lt;main&gt;</code>, <code data-start="194" data-end="204">&lt;footer&gt;</code> are present</p>
</li>
<li data-start="217" data-end="286">
<p data-start="219" data-end="286"><code data-start="219" data-end="228">&lt;table&gt;</code> has <code data-start="233" data-end="244">&lt;caption&gt;</code>, <code data-start="246" data-end="255">&lt;thead&gt;</code>, <code data-start="257" data-end="275">&lt;th scope="col"&gt;</code>, <code data-start="277" data-end="286">&lt;tbody&gt;</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="288" data-end="291">
<h2 data-start="293" data-end="351">⚠️ <strong data-start="299" data-end="351">But here’s what might cause the checker to fail:</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="353" data-end="387">1️⃣ <strong data-start="361" data-end="387">h2 Tag Inside <code data-start="377" data-end="385">&lt;main&gt;</code></strong></h3>
<ul data-start="388" data-end="586">
<li data-start="388" data-end="497">
<p data-start="390" data-end="497">The checker <strong data-start="402" data-end="496">might expect ONLY the <code data-start="426" data-end="435">&lt;table&gt;</code> inside <code data-start="443" data-end="451">&lt;main&gt;</code>, or it’s very strict on headings structure</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="498" data-end="586">
<p data-start="500" data-end="586"><strong data-start="500" data-end="586">Try removing the <code data-start="519" data-end="544">&lt;h2&gt;Event Schedule&lt;/h2&gt;</code> temporarily to see if that’s the issue.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="588" data-end="596"><strong data-start="588" data-end="596">Fix:</strong></p>
