</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1003" data-end="1006">
<h3 data-start="1008" data-end="1051">3️⃣ <strong data-start="1016" data-end="1051">Double Check Footer Consistency</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1052" data-end="1154">
<li data-start="1052" data-end="1154">
<p data-start="1054" data-end="1154">The <strong data-start="1058" data-end="1073">footer text</strong> should be <strong data-start="1084" data-end="1095">EXACTLY</strong> the same on <strong data-start="1108" data-end="1153">index.html, about.html, and schedule.html</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1156" data-end="1164">Example:</p>
