    </span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;</span><span><span class="hljs-symbol">&amp;copy;</span></span><span> 2024 TechCon. All rights reserved.</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">p</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">footer</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<ul data-start="1249" data-end="1385">
<li data-start="1249" data-end="1385">
<p data-start="1251" data-end="1385">Go and <strong data-start="1258" data-end="1294">open your index.html, about.html</strong>, and <strong data-start="1300" data-end="1311">compare</strong> the <code data-start="1316" data-end="1326">&lt;footer&gt;</code> to confirm that <strong data-start="1343" data-end="1384">it’s identical character by character</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ul>
