</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="244" data-end="352">➡️ <strong data-start="247" data-end="319">The checker is specifically looking for the word <code data-start="298" data-end="309">copyright</code> in text</strong>, <em data-start="321" data-end="352">not just the <code data-start="335" data-end="343">&amp;copy;</code> symbol.</em></p>
<hr data-start="354" data-end="357">
<h3 data-start="359" data-end="383">✅ <strong data-start="365" data-end="383">How to fix it:</strong></h3>
<p data-start="384" data-end="468">Make sure <strong data-start="394" data-end="457">your footer <em data-start="408" data-end="414">text</em> explicitly includes the word <code data-start="444" data-end="455">copyright</code></strong> like this:</p>
