</span><span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">footer</span></span></span><span>&gt;
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<ul data-start="558" data-end="701">
<li data-start="558" data-end="600">
<p data-start="560" data-end="600"><strong data-start="560" data-end="599">See? “Copyright” is now spelled out</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="601" data-end="701">
<p data-start="603" data-end="701"><strong data-start="603" data-end="638">Avoid using just <code data-start="622" data-end="630">&amp;copy;</code> alone</strong> for the checker unless your course instructions say otherwise.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="703" data-end="706">
