<hr data-start="2596" data-end="2599">
<h3 data-start="2601" data-end="2631">❗ <strong data-start="2607" data-end="2630">Notice what changed</strong>:</h3>
<p data-start="2632" data-end="2708">✔ <strong data-start="2634" data-end="2659">Lowercase <code data-start="2646" data-end="2657">copyright</code></strong> → <code data-start="2662" data-end="2708">copyright 2024 TechCon. All rights reserved.</code></p>
<p data-start="2710" data-end="2787">Some checkers <strong data-start="2724" data-end="2732">fail</strong> when you use <code data-start="2746" data-end="2757">Copyright</code> with uppercase or <code data-start="2776" data-end="2779">©</code> symbol.</p>
