</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="161" data-end="181"><strong data-start="161" data-end="181">What this means:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="182" data-end="520">
<li data-start="182" data-end="281">
<p data-start="184" data-end="281">Your <strong data-start="189" data-end="212">Ubuntu WSL terminal</strong> is <strong data-start="216" data-end="249">unable to access the internet</strong> to download the VS Code Server.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="282" data-end="520">
<p data-start="284" data-end="353">This <strong data-start="289" data-end="331">“Temporary failure in name resolution”</strong> usually happens when:</p>
<ol data-start="356" data-end="520">
<li data-start="356" data-end="394">
<p data-start="359" data-end="394"><strong data-start="359" data-end="393">WSL’s network is misconfigured</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="397" data-end="455">
<p data-start="400" data-end="455">Your <strong data-start="405" data-end="454">internet connection is unstable or restricted</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="458" data-end="520">
<p data-start="461" data-end="520"><strong data-start="461" data-end="475">DNS server</strong> in WSL is broken or not properly configured.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="522" data-end="525">
<h2 data-start="527" data-end="567">✅ <strong data-start="532" data-end="567">Step-by-Step Fix for This Error</strong></h2>
<h3 data-start="569" data-end="619">1️⃣ <strong data-start="577" data-end="619">Check that Windows itself has Internet</strong></h3>
<p data-start="620" data-end="723">Before fixing WSL, open <strong data-start="644" data-end="654">Chrome</strong> or <strong data-start="658" data-end="666">Edge</strong> on Windows and confirm that you can visit websites like:</p>
<ul data-start="724" data-end="787">
<li data-start="724" data-end="748">
<p data-start="726" data-end="748"><a data-start="726" data-end="748" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="" href="https://www.google.com/">https://www.google.com</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="749" data-end="787">
<p data-start="751" data-end="787"><a data-start="751" data-end="787" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="" href="https://update.code.visualstudio.com/">https://update.code.visualstudio.com</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="789" data-end="838">If they load, <strong data-start="803" data-end="837">the problem is only inside WSL</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="840" data-end="843">
<h3 data-start="845" data-end="879">2️⃣ <strong data-start="853" data-end="879">Restart WSL Completely</strong></h3>
<p data-start="880" data-end="958">Run this command <strong data-start="897" data-end="958">in your Windows CMD/PowerShell (outside Ubuntu terminal):</strong></p>
