<h3 data-start="1049" data-end="1094">3️⃣ <strong data-start="1057" data-end="1094">Fix DNS for WSL (Recommended Fix)</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1095" data-end="1177">If it still fails, <strong data-start="1114" data-end="1162">manually configure WSL to use a reliable DNS</strong> like Google’s:</p>
<h4 data-start="1179" data-end="1222">✅ Steps to manually configure WSL DNS:</h4>
<ol data-start="1223" data-end="1254">
<li data-start="1223" data-end="1254">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1254">In <strong data-start="1229" data-end="1248">Ubuntu terminal</strong>, run:</p>
