<hr data-start="1875" data-end="1878">
<h3 data-start="1880" data-end="1927">5️⃣ <strong data-start="1888" data-end="1927">Try Installing VS Code Server Again</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1928" data-end="1961">After doing the above steps, try:</p>
