<ul data-start="646" data-end="786">
<li data-start="646" data-end="769">
<p data-start="648" data-end="769">If <strong data-start="651" data-end="672">ping doesn’t work</strong>, your WSL can’t connect to the internet — you need to <strong data-start="727" data-end="743">fix your DNS</strong> like I explained earlier.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="770" data-end="786">
<p data-start="772" data-end="786">Fix DNS using:</p>
</li>
</ul>
