</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="870" data-end="888">Save and close it.</p>
<hr data-start="890" data-end="893">
<h3 data-start="895" data-end="918">2️⃣ <strong data-start="903" data-end="918">Restart WSL</strong></h3>
<p data-start="919" data-end="967">Run in <strong data-start="926" data-end="940">PowerShell</strong> or <strong data-start="944" data-end="951">CMD</strong> on <strong data-start="955" data-end="966">Windows</strong>:</p>
