<ul data-start="361" data-end="506">
<li data-start="361" data-end="506">
<p data-start="363" data-end="506">It’s <strong data-start="368" data-end="426">showing that your WSL (Ubuntu) can access the internet</strong>, <strong data-start="428" data-end="473">but with some network lag/delay (high ms)</strong>. That’s why you see things like:</p>
</li>
</ul>
