<p data-start="548" data-end="625">→ <strong data-start="550" data-end="625">9671 ms = 9.6 seconds → That’s a very slow response, but still working.</strong></p>
<hr data-start="627" data-end="630">
<h3 data-start="632" data-end="673">✅ <strong data-start="638" data-end="673">How to stop the infinity output</strong></h3>
<p data-start="674" data-end="763">Press <strong data-start="680" data-end="694"><code data-start="682" data-end="692">CTRL + C</code></strong> on your keyboard.<br>
It will stop the ping and give you a summary like:</p>
