</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="808" data-end="811">
<h3 data-start="813" data-end="839">📌 <strong data-start="820" data-end="839">Why is it slow?</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="840" data-end="1040">
<li data-start="840" data-end="913">
<p data-start="842" data-end="913">Your <strong data-start="847" data-end="882">internet connection is unstable</strong> or slow in WSL at that moment.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="914" data-end="989">
<p data-start="916" data-end="989">Could be <strong data-start="925" data-end="943">network issues</strong> on your Wi-Fi or DNS resolution delay in WSL.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="990" data-end="1040">
<p data-start="992" data-end="1040">Might work fine later or on a better connection.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1042" data-end="1045">
<h3 data-start="1047" data-end="1084">🟢 <strong data-start="1054" data-end="1084">Next Step → What to do now</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1134">Since <strong data-start="1091" data-end="1119">your internet is working</strong>, even if slow:</p>
<ol data-start="1136" data-end="1212">
<li data-start="1136" data-end="1169">
<p data-start="1139" data-end="1169"><strong data-start="1139" data-end="1169">Stop the ping → <code data-start="1157" data-end="1167">CTRL + C</code></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1170" data-end="1212">
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1212">Retry <strong data-start="1179" data-end="1205">VS Code WSL connection</strong> → Run:</p>
</li>
</ol>
