This project is part of the HTML &amp; CSS curriculum at ALX Software Engineering.

</span><span><span class="hljs-section">## Objectives</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span></span><span> Practice advanced CSS styling techniques
</span><span><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span></span><span> Implement a web page design using a Figma prototype
</span><span><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span></span><span> Ensure HTML and CSS code are valid using W3C validators

</span><span><span class="hljs-section">## Resources</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-strong">**Figma Design**</span></span><span>: https://www.figma.com/file/KCSbYso8BbsJsTUEG3rACa/alx</span><span><span class="hljs-emphasis">_html_</span></span><span>css
</span><span><span class="hljs-bullet">-</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-strong">**Images**</span></span><span>: https://github.com/alx-tools/0x02-CSS<span class="hljs-emphasis">_advanced/tree/main/images
- </span></span><span><span class="hljs-strong">**Fonts**</span></span><span>:
  - [</span><span><span class="hljs-string">Source Sans Pro</span></span><span>](</span><span><span class="hljs-link">https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Source+Sans+Pro</span></span><span>)
  - [</span><span><span class="hljs-string">Spin Cycle OT</span></span><span>](</span><span><span class="hljs-link">https://www.fonts.com/font/spin-cycle-ot</span></span><span>)

## Requirements

- No external CSS or JS frameworks (no Bootstrap, no React, etc.)
- Files must end with a new line
- HTML and CSS must validate via W3C validator

## Author

- Your Name
- GitHub: [</span><span><span class="hljs-string">@YourUsername</span></span><span>](</span><span><span class="hljs-link">https://github.com/YourUsername</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1450" data-end="1480">✅ <strong data-start="1452" data-end="1480">SAVE the file (CTRL + S)</strong></p>
