<h2 data-start="2436" data-end="2483">✅ <strong data-start="2441" data-end="2483">STAGE 6 (Optional for now): Next Steps</strong></h2>
<ol data-start="2484" data-end="2770">
<li data-start="2484" data-end="2574">
<p data-start="2487" data-end="2574">Download images from:<br>
→ <a data-start="2511" data-end="2574" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="" href="https://github.com/alx-tools/0x02-CSS_advanced/tree/main/images">https://github.com/alx-tools/0x02-CSS_advanced/tree/main/images</a></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2576" data-end="2703">
<p data-start="2579" data-end="2703">Open the <strong data-start="2588" data-end="2604">Figma design</strong> to start copying the page layout:<br>
