<hr data-start="1179" data-end="1182">
<h2 data-start="1184" data-end="1228">🟢 <strong data-start="1190" data-end="1228">STEP 5: What Next After This Task?</strong></h2>
<p data-start="1229" data-end="1256">After <strong data-start="1235" data-end="1245">Task 0</strong>, you will:</p>
<ol data-start="1257" data-end="1443">
<li data-start="1257" data-end="1322">
<p data-start="1260" data-end="1322">Start building the <strong data-start="1279" data-end="1294">actual page</strong> using the <strong data-start="1305" data-end="1321">Figma design</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1323" data-end="1372">
<p data-start="1326" data-end="1372"><strong data-start="1326" data-end="1349">Create a styles.css</strong> file to hold your CSS.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1373" data-end="1443">
<p data-start="1376" data-end="1443">Write the <strong data-start="1386" data-end="1404">HTML structure</strong> in index.html to match the Figma file.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1445" data-end="1505">➡ <strong data-start="1447" data-end="1496">Want help creating the next part of the page?</strong> Tell me:</p>
<ul data-start="1506" data-end="1609">
<li data-start="1506" data-end="1564">
<p data-start="1508" data-end="1564">✅ “Give me step-by-step to build the page from Figma”<br>
or</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1565" data-end="1609">
<p data-start="1567" data-end="1609">✅ “Give me the starter CSS and structure.”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1611" data-end="1614">
