al [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="151">Excellent — <strong data-start="12" data-end="37">let’s go step by step</strong> to help you <strong data-start="50" data-end="81">complete this task properly</strong>. I’ll break it <strong data-start="97" data-end="108">clearly</strong> for you, with the <strong data-start="127" data-end="141">exact code</strong> you need.</p>
<hr data-start="153" data-end="156">
<h2 data-start="158" data-end="199">✅ <strong data-start="163" data-end="199">1️⃣ Create the <code data-start="180" data-end="192">styles.css</code> file</strong></h2>
<p data-start="201" data-end="235">In your <strong data-start="209" data-end="227"><code data-start="211" data-end="225">css_advanced</code></strong> folder:</p>
