</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="265" data-end="322">OR in VS Code → <strong data-start="281" data-end="322">Right-click → New File → <code data-start="308" data-end="320">styles.css</code></strong></p>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327">
<h2 data-start="329" data-end="384">✅ <strong data-start="334" data-end="384">2️⃣ Link <code data-start="345" data-end="357">styles.css</code> inside your <code data-start="370" data-end="382">index.html</code></strong></h2>
<p data-start="386" data-end="473">Open <strong data-start="391" data-end="407"><code data-start="393" data-end="405">index.html</code></strong> and inside the <code data-start="423" data-end="431">&lt;head&gt;</code> tag, <strong data-start="437" data-end="454">add this line</strong> to import the CSS:</p>
