<hr data-start="760" data-end="763">
<h3 data-start="765" data-end="811">✅ <strong data-start="771" data-end="811">When should you replace it entirely?</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="812" data-end="981">
<li data-start="812" data-end="905">
<p data-start="814" data-end="905">Only if you <strong data-start="826" data-end="860">don’t have the right structure</strong> or if your current file <strong data-start="885" data-end="904">is empty/broken</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="906" data-end="981">
<p data-start="908" data-end="981">Otherwise → <strong data-start="920" data-end="981">keep yours → just import the CSS using that <code data-start="966" data-end="974">&lt;link&gt;</code> tag.</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="983" data-end="986">
<p data-start="988" data-end="1019">⚙ <strong data-start="990" data-end="1019">Next Step Help Available:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1020" data-end="1235">
<li data-start="1020" data-end="1118">
<p data-start="1022" data-end="1118">Need help to clean up or complete <strong data-start="1056" data-end="1083">your exact <code data-start="1069" data-end="1081">index.html</code></strong> → just <strong data-start="1091" data-end="1117">send me your file/code</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1119" data-end="1235">
<p data-start="1121" data-end="1235">Want <strong data-start="1126" data-end="1161">help building your <code data-start="1147" data-end="1159">styles.css</code></strong> → just say <strong data-start="1173" data-end="1203">“Let’s build the real CSS”</strong> → I’ll help step by step again.</p>
</li>
</ul>
