essage-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p data-start="0" data-end="214">Great — <strong data-start="8" data-end="33">let’s go step by step</strong> and I’ll help you <strong data-start="52" data-end="92">style the Header and Banner properly</strong> for this task, using <strong data-start="114" data-end="143">Figma design as reference</strong> (with general values since I don’t have your actual Figma draft open).</p>
<p data-start="216" data-end="319">Here’s a <strong data-start="225" data-end="245">complete example</strong> of <strong data-start="249" data-end="292">what your <code data-start="261" data-end="273">styles.css</code> should look like</strong> for the header and banner:</p>
