code .
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1022" data-end="1025">
<h3 data-start="1027" data-end="1083">Option B: You want to create a new repo from VS Code</h3>
<ol data-start="1085" data-end="1260">
<li data-start="1085" data-end="1100">
<p data-start="1088" data-end="1100">Open VS Code</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1101" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1104" data-end="1146">Create a new folder (e.g., <code data-start="1131" data-end="1145">alx_html_css</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1147" data-end="1241">
<p data-start="1150" data-end="1179">Open the terminal in VS Code:</p>
<ul data-start="1183" data-end="1241">
<li data-start="1183" data-end="1241">
<p data-start="1185" data-end="1241">Press <code data-start="1191" data-end="1201">CTRL + ~</code> (tilde) or go to Menu → View → Terminal</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="1242" data-end="1260">
<p data-start="1245" data-end="1260">Initialize Git:</p>
</li>
</ol>
