<ol start="5" data-start="1284" data-end="1366">
<li data-start="1284" data-end="1334">
<p data-start="1287" data-end="1334">Create a file (e.g., <code data-start="1308" data-end="1320">index.html</code>, <code data-start="1322" data-end="1333">README.md</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1335" data-end="1366">
<p data-start="1338" data-end="1366">Add your remote GitHub repo:</p>
</li>
</ol>
