</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2467" data-end="2620">If you don’t have real images yet, just use any placeholder images <strong data-start="2534" data-end="2560">with the correct names</strong> (<code data-start="2562" data-end="2572">logo.png</code>, <code data-start="2574" data-end="2586">banner.jpg</code>) or use image links from the web.</p>
<hr data-start="2622" data-end="2625">
<h2 data-start="2627" data-end="2649">✅ 4. Push to GitHub</h2>
