<h3 data-start="3361" data-end="3391">⚠ <strong data-start="3367" data-end="3391">Is this clearer now?</strong></h3>
<p data-start="3392" data-end="3420">I broke it down very slowly.</p>
<p data-start="3422" data-end="3516">➔ If you want, I can <strong data-start="3443" data-end="3477">guide you while you do it live</strong> — Just tell me <strong data-start="3493" data-end="3515">where you’re stuck</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="3517" data-end="3640">
<li data-start="3517" data-end="3562">
<p data-start="3519" data-end="3562">You don’t know how to create folders/files?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3563" data-end="3604">
<p data-start="3565" data-end="3604">You don’t know how to use the terminal?</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3605" data-end="3640">
<p data-start="3607" data-end="3640">You don’t know how to use GitHub?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3642" data-end="3718">Tell me exactly where to <strong data-start="3667" data-end="3681">focus help</strong>, and we’ll solve it together 👩🏽‍💻</p>
