g> (the one you didn’t understand).</p>
<hr data-start="112" data-end="115">
<h2 data-start="117" data-end="158">✅ <strong data-start="122" data-end="158">STEP 4: Add Images (if you have)</strong></h2>
<p data-start="160" data-end="229">This step is <strong data-start="173" data-end="207">about adding pictures (images)</strong> to your project like:</p>
<ul data-start="231" data-end="345">
<li data-start="231" data-end="271">
<p data-start="233" data-end="271">a <strong data-start="235" data-end="243">logo</strong> for the header (<code data-start="260" data-end="270">logo.png</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="272" data-end="345">
<p data-start="274" data-end="345">a <strong data-start="276" data-end="296">background image</strong> for the banner (<code data-start="313" data-end="325">banner.jpg</code> — optional for now)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="347" data-end="398">🟨 Here's What It Means (in very simple terms):</h3>
<p data-start="400" data-end="434">Your folder should look like this:</p>
