<hr data-start="711" data-end="714">
<h2 data-start="716" data-end="750">🛠️ How to Do It — Step-by-Step</h2>
<h3 data-start="752" data-end="791">✅ <strong data-start="758" data-end="791">1. Create the <code data-start="774" data-end="782">images</code> folder</strong></h3>
<p data-start="792" data-end="803">In VS Code:</p>
<ul data-start="804" data-end="946">
<li data-start="804" data-end="843">
<p data-start="806" data-end="843">Look at your left sidebar (Explorer).</p>
</li>
<li data-start="844" data-end="901">
<p data-start="846" data-end="901"><strong data-start="846" data-end="884">Right-click on your project folder</strong> (<code data-start="886" data-end="900">css_advanced</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="902" data-end="926">
<p data-start="904" data-end="926">Click <strong data-start="910" data-end="926">"New Folder"</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="927" data-end="946">
<p data-start="929" data-end="946">Name it: <code data-start="938" data-end="946">images</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="948" data-end="951">
<h3 data-start="953" data-end="982">✅ <strong data-start="959" data-end="982">2. Add a Logo Image</strong></h3>
<p data-start="984" data-end="1021">If you already have a <strong data-start="1006" data-end="1020">logo image</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start="1022" data-end="1140">
<li data-start="1022" data-end="1049">
<p data-start="1024" data-end="1049">Save it to your computer.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1050" data-end="1109">
<p data-start="1052" data-end="1109">Then <strong data-start="1057" data-end="1093">drag it into the <code data-start="1076" data-end="1084">images</code> folder</strong> inside VS Code.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1110" data-end="1140">
<p data-start="1112" data-end="1140">Rename it to: <strong data-start="1126" data-end="1140"><code data-start="1128" data-end="1138">logo.png</code></strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1142" data-end="1167">If you don't have a logo:</p>
<ul data-start="1168" data-end="1230">
<li data-start="1168" data-end="1230">
<p data-start="1170" data-end="1230">You can download a free logo online or use this placeholder:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1352">👉 Right-click to download: <a data-start="1260" data-end="1352" class="cursor-pointer" rel="noopener" target="_new">Right-click &amp; Save This Logo</a></p>
<hr data-start="1354" data-end="1357">
<h3 data-start="1359" data-end="1412">✅ <strong data-start="1365" data-end="1412">3. (Optional) Add a Banner Background Image</strong></h3>
<p data-start="1414" data-end="1476">If you also have a banner image (like a big background image):</p>
<ul data-start="1477" data-end="1537">
<li data-start="1477" data-end="1513">
<p data-start="1479" data-end="1513">Put it in the <code data-start="1493" data-end="1501">images</code> folder too.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1514" data-end="1537">
<p data-start="1516" data-end="1537">Name it: <code data-start="1525" data-end="1537">banner.jpg</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1539" data-end="1655">But if you don’t have one now, <strong data-start="1570" data-end="1583">it’s okay</strong>. We'll just keep a plain color in the banner (already done in the CSS).</p>
<hr data-start="1657" data-end="1660">
<h3 data-start="1662" data-end="1675">✅ 4. Done</h3>
<p data-start="1677" data-end="1736">That’s it! You now have the correct folder and image setup.</p>
<hr data-start="1738" data-end="1741">
<h3 data-start="1743" data-end="1770">💡 Now You Can Continue</h3>
<p data-start="1772" data-end="1886">Once your <code data-start="1782" data-end="1791">images/</code> folder has <code data-start="1803" data-end="1813">logo.png</code>, the HTML will show the logo correctly, and CSS will style it as needed.</p>
<hr data-start="1888" data-end="1891">
<p data-start="1893" data-end="1973">Would you like me to <strong data-start="1914" data-end="1955">send you a free logo and banner image</strong> to use right now?</p>
<p data-start="1975" data-end="2042">Or do you want help <strong data-start="1995" data-end="2030">dragging images into the folder</strong> in VS Code?</p>
<p data-start="2044" data-end="2096" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just say the word — I’ll stay with you through it 😊</p></div></div></div></div><button class="btn relative btn-primary mt-4 self-start" data-testid="paragen-prefer-response-button"><div class="flex items-center justify-center">I prefer this response</div></button></div></div><div data-paragen-root="true" class="@container relative flex min-w-[min(450px,80cqw,80vw)] flex-1 snap-center flex-col gap-1 text-start border-token-border-tertiary rounded-xl border shadow-lg shadow-black/3"><div class="[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin) py-4"><div class="absolute top-48 right-0! left-0! h-px invisible"></div><div class="absolute top-48 right-0! bottom-0 left-0! invisible"></div><div class="absolute right-0! bottom-0 left-0! h-px invisible"></div><div class="flex gap-4 items-center mb-1"><div><div class="pt-0"><div class="gizmo-bot-avatar flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full"><div class="relative flex items-center justify-center h-6 w-6 shrink-0 rounded-xs bg-token-main-surface-primary text-token-text-primary"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon"><text x="-9999" y="-9999">ChatGPT</text><path d="M9.20509 8.76511V6.50545C9.20509 6.31513 9.27649 6.17234 9.44293 6.0773L13.9861 3.46088C14.6046 3.10413 15.342 2.93769 16.103 2.93769C18.9573 2.93769 20.7651 5.14983 20.7651 7.50454C20.7651 7.67098 20.7651 7.86129 20.7412 8.05161L16.0316 5.2924C15.7462 5.12596 15.4607 5.12596 15.1753 5.2924L9.20509 8.76511ZM19.8135 17.5659V12.1664C19.8135 11.8333 19.6708 11.5955 19.3854 11.429L13.4152 7.95633L15.3656 6.83833C15.5321 6.74328 15.6749 6.74328 15.8413 6.83833L20.3845 9.45474C21.6928 10.216 22.5728 11.8333 22.5728 13.4031C22.5728 15.2108 21.5025 16.8758 19.8135 17.5657V17.5659ZM7.8017